calling-an-api_key2: `API` humne abhi samjha kya hote hai. Ab hum ek `API` ko `call` kar kar kuch data mangwayenge.
calling-an-api_key4: iss link ko open karo. SARAL ke server par yeh data hai, jo hum iss course mei use karenge.
calling-an-api_key5: Abhi ke liye, humei ek bahut simple sa `code` likhna hai.
calling-an-api_key9: `call` hum `functions` ke liye bhi use karte hai. functions ko hum karte hai, kuch `arguments` dete hai, aur kuch vapas lete hai (jo function `return` karta hai)
calling-an-api_key10: `API` ko bhi aap aise function ki tarah soch sakte hai, jo server ne aapko diya hai, use karne ke liye. Aap usse `call` karoge, kuch `arguments` doge, aur woh aapko kuch `json` ya kisi aur `format` mei `data` `return` kar dega
calling-an-api_key11: `json` sabse commonly used data format hai, jismei server `data` `return` karta hai. Pehle `xml` kaafi popular format tha, data exchange ka
